'''Naboo houseboats''' were wooden boats inhabited by swamp dwellers of all sorts. Located in the [[Naboo/Legends|Naboo]] Bayou and the Naboo Swamps, the boats were old-fashioned, wheel-powered river boats that had living quarters on board.

==Battle for Naboo==
During the Trade Federation blockade, the boats were unhesitatingly attacked by [[Droid/Legends|droid]] fighters and bombers, largely due to the fact that they were easily destructible being made of wood. Captain [[Kael (officer)|Kael]] and [[Gavyn Sykes/Legends|Gavyn Sykes]] had escaped from [[Theed/Legends|Theed]] and came to aid the fleeing houseboats in [[N-X Police Cruiser/Legends|N-X Police Cruisers]]. They eventually drove the droid fighters off, earning the help of Naboo Swamp dweller [[Vedd Deviss]].

==Behind the scenes==
They were inspired by real life steamboats which are found in swamp areas in the Southeastern United States.

